title: Week 2 NFL Recap: Injuries dominate the Sunday discussion as Saquon Barkley, Nick Bosa go down (Football 9/21)
description:
Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson and John Breech link up to break down all the Sunday action from Week 2 of the 2020 NFL season. Unfortunately, it was a day headlined by injuries to several big-name players including Saquon Barkley and Nick Bosa. The guys break down the rash of injuries before going game-by-game with their breakdowns.
